    <div class="strilli" style="margin-left: 30px; width: 251px; float:left;">
    <h5 style="margin-top: 1.5em"><span lang="en-gb"><font color="#006600"><span style="font-size: 90%">Rednex Cownex</span></font></span></h5>
      <p>The <strong>CowNex simulator</strong> created by INRA for the RedNex project is used to calculate  protein synthesis and nitrogen excretion in a dairy cattle herd, including  heifers, depending on herd management.<br />
        It performs these calculations  throughout the year and measures the impact of management changes, particularly  nutrition, on the efficiency of nitrogen use by the herd and the release of  fecal or urine nitrogen.<br />
        To  access the simulator and user guide go to <a href="http://www.cownex-record.inra.fr" target="_blank">www.cownex-record.inra.fr</a>. To  register a username and password click <strong>Subscription</strong>.<br /><br />
For further information please contact <a href="mailto:cownex@rennes.inra.fr">cownex@rennes.inra.fr</a></p></div></div></div>
